     C* D2: data-structure redefinition of an existing alphameric field.
     C* REC1 (EDATA position 1, value '0') is redefined by DS REC1; its
     C* subfield X (position 1) must read the SAME physical byte.
     FEDATA   IP  F    80              DISK
     IEDATA       AA
     I                                        1   1 REC1
     IREC1        DS
     I                                        1   1 X
     C           X         COMP '0'                      10
     C  10                 Z-ADD1         RPGRET
